work.work-title: I know that my Redeemer lives

credit.credit-words: He lives to bless me with His love, He lives to plead for me above. He lives my hungry soul to feed, He lives to help in time of need.
I know that my Redeemer lives
He lives, all glory to His name! He lives, my Jesus, still the same. Oh, the sweet joy this sentence gives, I know that my redeemer lives!
